{"tid":1470384,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"關於呢幾日我有野想講","createTime":"2019-08-14T05:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T10:53:53.000Z","uid":169495,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bb17c8f9a469bcff2eb0abfae47f05c3be9c2fdf","tid":1470384,"uid":169495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:10:23.000Z","msg":"1. <span style=\"color: gold;\">癱瘓機場無錯, 但唔可以係我地做主動去塞</span> ,<br />\n用人海, 係機管局handle唔到咁多人而停, 唔係我地令人地無飛機坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. <span style=\"color: gold;\">道歉可以, 但唔係為打公安而道歉</span>, 最多認自己衝動7左。Sorry對象係FA , 記者, 同受影響旅客。<br />\n3. 連續兩日搞機場, 我地只係搞緊同一班8000人, 點解唔可以隔幾日, 搞另一堆8000人, <span style=\"color: gold;\">比尋日D人飛左先,效果會唔會大好多(16000人)又少啲人嘈你? </span><br />\n4. 唔好代示威者應承任何野, 同FA , 記者講Sorry係道德同良知上出發, <span style=\"color: gold;\">加上日後可以屌番對家道歉都唔撚識。</span><br />\n5. 我會覺得今晚唔好又成大人班去機場, 比受影響果班人走左先, 留個頭版比醫護人員, 佢地呢幾日其實好撚勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,好中五大訴求但比我地distract左<br />\n<br />\n6. (提防散水黨?) 走唔走問自己幾個問題, <span style=\"color: gold;\">今日目標係咩, 目的係咩</span><br />\nE.g. 入機場 目標係癱瘓機場, 目的無論任何時候都係五大<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">當目標達到左, 就唔需要守, 說好的hit and run 呀!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(唔好賴底前線) 走唔走係個人選擇,唔係有人唔肯走你就一定要留, 你如果你決定走, 話比前線知, 佢地都會自己判斷, 唔好等佢地轉頭先唔見晒人, 話自己走啦同拉人下齊走係唔同架。走都唔代表係番屋企訓, <span style=\"color: gold;\">可以轉場架</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 明白遍地開花,勇武和理非互補。 但大家出去課外活動前都應該諗一諗聽日新聞大家想見到咩。 有時課外活動重疊左個訴求反而唔夠出。<br />\n衝突+衝突=加成<br />\n和平+衝突=模糊左<br />\nE.g. 塞鐵+罷工, 醫護罷工+塞機場, <br />\n所以如果和平野同有機會變衝突嘅係同一日, 我建議揀一個集中。讓個頭版比佢。大家都知道有衝突果陣就好容易比對家spin, 和平雖然無可能迫到對方表態但句句都會中到五大, 準備/醞釀時間長<span style=\"color: gold;\">,唔係成日都搞得成, 但一做到就係好大支強心針補晒血</span>,e.g.銀髮遊行。唔好浪費個宣傳機會。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8. 捉鬼。其實無必要。而家班狗都認左自己滲透左示威者, <del>其實發生任何事都可以入佢地數</del>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n狗煽動示威者打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。狗煽動示威者衝擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。狗煽動示威者用魔法液<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。狗煽動示威者塞隧道<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。而家我地點講佢都解釋唔到架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 點解要懷疑自己人? 佢地保護左前線就真啦。真係比我地捉到隻餓底狗嘅, 唔好打佢, 同佢係記者前面搭膊頭, 講佢好有領導才能<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當日發生過嘅所有事都唔駛入示威者數。<br />\n9. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">核爆都唔割! </span></span>做錯左咪一齊認衰仔, 一班人一齊認同推幾個前線去認效果好唔同。中學無打過交咩? <span style=\"color: gold;\">如果成班人都話自己錯, 咁就變成老師錯架啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 認完就推個波去政府,成件事都係佢地唔回應先搞到班人咁嬲。 雖然我係打從心底覺得公安死左都唔抵可憐, 不過要手足雙手沾到佢D低等生物臭血就真係唔想囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。下次再有同樣事情大家醒目啲(<del>開傘遮住幾秒</del>)就分開佢啦。<br />\n10.上面9點我都只係聽到有狗講, 我轉述炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢話千其唔好咁做, 我都係咁覺得"},{"pid":"07de06050b69c076a070968982c41a6d5dfc4d21","tid":1470384,"uid":169495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:14:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"98d067c88052e6ceb3c269263b7f80668cefbeaf","tid":1470384,"uid":169495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:14:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">復</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"05c26d65cb88b4819d674517d5e37c8cb76c6fb7","tid":1470384,"uid":169495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:15:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e4e83296479bb8712981595b4891728d507c0562","tid":1470384,"uid":169495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:15:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">港</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d129ec5e0ebe69197a88d8b1b2c6c74fa79f4f54","tid":1470384,"uid":169495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:15:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">時</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"eaefb718a5baf58ab603fee848769be954c3a101","tid":1470384,"uid":169495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:16:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">代</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"13a52937209daaffd3992f016f421995d7c5fe85","tid":1470384,"uid":169495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:16:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">革</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"47a8cc05088caaed488e3e681b0964fda968db25","tid":1470384,"uid":169495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:16:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"18c6eb6fe2aff83438a9c6c4d8f348f026cbd0dc","tid":1470384,"uid":37894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:17:34.000Z","msg":"我地應該每星期搵一日，同一個時間一齊搭車入機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468945</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2046f3d7a380a8f8f382704df7ed27d78ccc947e","tid":1470384,"uid":169495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18c6eb6fe2aff83438a9c6c4d8f348f026cbd0dc","tid":1470384,"uid":37894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:17:34.000Z","msg":"我地應該每星期搵一日，同一個時間一齊搭車入機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468945</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:17:56.000Z","msg":"推吵"},{"pid":"ac05